Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:13.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底知れぬ深い海でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:19.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　波を蹴って虹架けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:25.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　今じゃなくちゃ出来ないから!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうでもないような日常でバッタリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間的な闘争本能ではったり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:36.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船飛んで来て銀河外交…なんてね!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほっぺた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（つねっても）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛い…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（夢じゃない）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:47.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実のほうがかなりスリル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退屈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（したくない）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:53.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（夢を見よ）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗でも主役級　ド迫力だい!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空に疾風　吹かせてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:10.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青い自転車きしませて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.21,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あざ笑う急勾配に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　傷つく勇気　見つける旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:27.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　急かす今と走り出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:13.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是深不可测的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:19.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　也要冲破风浪越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:25.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　因为只有现在才能做到!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在无聊的平日里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用瞬间的斗争本能虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:36.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和飞来的宇宙船做银河外交…怎么可能呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（掐一下）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（不是梦）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:47.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实世界相当刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（不想那样）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:53.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（去做梦吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失败也是主角级的超级气魄!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中卷起旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:10.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱动蓝色的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑那陡坡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　每当发现受伤的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:27.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　与匆忙的现在一起出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:33.24,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　追い風を追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:40.93,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしなく　過去から未来まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.78,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミを守る！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.55,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life　コラボレーション
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:01.39,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミとボクはメビウスのコンビネーション
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.39,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love　運命事情↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:08.92,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複雑→心拍数上昇↑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:13.98,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失うことが怖いんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.68,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あきらめたりしたくないそれだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:24.41,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミとの約束があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.54,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:34.71,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠久で見たようなめぐり逢い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.62,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神のミステイク？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:42.45,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　向かい風向かってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:50.10,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しいStageを目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.63,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}キミと行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:33.24,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　乘着风追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:40.93,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有终点　从过去到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.78,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远守护着你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.55,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life　共同协作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:01.39,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与我有着无限的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.39,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love　因为命运↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:08.92,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复杂→心跳加快↑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:13.98,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.68,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:24.41,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和你有所约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.54,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:34.71,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠久而似曾相识的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.62,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的失误？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:42.45,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　迎着风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:50.10,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.63,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}与你一同迈进！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像最终回一样在完美的氛围中落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后接上一集的第二天早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是打了一天工  然后参加了一下咲夜小姐的生日聚会就倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不做做运动锻炼一下身体的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦…烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很柔弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们这些跟外表截然相反有无限体力的家伙可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…真的不要紧吗？  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不要紧  要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要叫医生来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚决不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还真丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐昨天已经那样努力过了  倒下也是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要这么宠着她好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是玛莉亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要生病  就不要挑春假的时候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新学期开学的时候倒下的话就能名正言顺地翘课了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  比想象中的要精神多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}因为是管家和大小姐的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出门去买东西  那孩子就交给你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  她昨天一天确实很努力了  倒下也是情有可原  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么之后就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒…小飒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  看她用那弱弱的声音喊着你呢  快点过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉咙很难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想喝苹果汁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  马上为您准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？玛莉亚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚小姐出门去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…克劳斯先生也出去了  要等明天才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球球和白野威也去了宠物之家作定期检查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就只有我们两个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到变成和小飒两个人独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小飒趁我生病不能动弹来推倒我的话该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后对我做这样那样的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道  连那种事情也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒的确是个很绅士的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈也跟我说过「男人都是披着羊皮的狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…  可是…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就回隔壁房间去了  有什么事的话请叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确没发生意外是好事…好歹你也要注意一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…一个人的话很寂寞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动弹又睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就留在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…生病的时候还是不要勉强  好好睡一觉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就想办法让我入睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…想办法让您入睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把自己原创的摇篮曲以MikuMiku的形式唱给您听…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宅方版Miku的UmaUma？睡得着才怪！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是多此一举吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这个  就没有别的方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样兴奋可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  讲故事怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人入睡的经典节目不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我当成小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…算了  我就暂且忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托选个有趣一点的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说经典的话  那就是「爱丽丝梦游仙境」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以「根绝战争」为目标的Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（刹那梦游仙境？Gundam OO的NETA就不多说了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝要进行武力介入吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了各种情节  爱丽丝她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到了不可思议的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像来到了个奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里究竟是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为突发事件而感到困惑的爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里遇到了向她搭讪的三个神秘的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀  没见过的脸孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那竟然是  会说话的兔子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是引路的兔子哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要不要我把出口告诉你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbits
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝同情地说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖肉角色还真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说的那么直白！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  要想到出口的话就要通过这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个会动的地面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下的话就会被带到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想原地不动的话就要全力奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想向前跑的话就必须要更加奋力地奔跑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将蕴含其中的社会规则毫无保留的暴露出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经典的试练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就赶去吧  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想到出口  就在这里全力跑起来给我们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话音未落  爱丽丝的身影已经消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  在那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于平时就比常人更加努力的爱丽丝来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度已经算不上是试练了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  单枪匹马就打倒了众多扑克牌士兵的爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达到了神奇王国的顶点  建立了新的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的名字叫做「合众国日本」  大家和平地生活了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（叛逆的鲁路修…）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺  可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里可喜可贺了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗  一点也没什么值得庆祝的  根本无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好用珍藏的结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听下回分解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没下回了  到B-Part再继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样了？小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小飒  就没有其它更有趣的书了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  有本「基于新粒子的发现的GN-Drive基础理论」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？伊奥利亚那老头是活在这个时代的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好休息才行  小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躺在床上做的已经全做了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新刊连载都看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新作GAME也都通关了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个时间段也没有动画在播放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因为这样  所以感冒才好不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  就算睡不着也给我躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒  我好无聊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我准备个能消磨3小时左右的有趣的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚂蚁观察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个小摄像头观察蚂蚁的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察蚂蚁有什么好玩的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packy啊Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉吃了Packy的话  马上就能睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在马上给我去买Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  只要是为了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领结歪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你到底是怎么了？突然说想吃Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  这比观察蚂蚁要有价值多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？居然用微型摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得会很有趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  Switch On！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子像是在追一只抢鱼的野猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免了无意义的杀生  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被卷进麻烦事里了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是「想去买个东西  于是来到城里」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（富士台的长篇动画“海螺小姐(サザエさん)”OP的歌词…）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子像是忘记带钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至于连这也和歌词一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？咲夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说些什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你穿着还真合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不得不给你加工钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只做1个小时而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我忘记带钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  回来拿一下不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  晚饭前一定将Packy给您买来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒真是让人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉露热茶两杯  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  伊澄  好可爱的女仆小姐哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？飒先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澄小姐和令堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会来人这么多的店里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从咲夜那拿到了这里的免费券哦  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好打了1小时工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样总算能回归正轨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再被卷进什么不幸事件中就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亘那家伙   有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  用我为了应付这种情况而学的读唇术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了应付怎样的情况而学的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前偷偷租给凪的《拜托了双子星》DVD  赶快还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:49.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（《おねがい★ツインズ》，中译《拜托了双子星》，\N《拜托了老师》的续篇。台湾代理商普威尔译为《星空的邂逅2》）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每集都有入浴的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但女孩子看了也不会高兴的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞒着我租了那种DVD啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  还是别管这个继续看小飒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又过了2小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人问路15次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助有麻烦的老年人23次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上因为强盗事件路被封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后碰上了那个强盗  并把他捉拿归案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还偶然地找到了团伙的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果到最后还…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我要买Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有货的话  我也想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是Packy这种小点心灭绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道  Packy还真有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来平时不注意社会潮流是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是Packy节！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吃Packy吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么今天突然想吃Packy了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到Packy是这么好吃的下酒菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是运气差到让人想哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚为小飒做一顿牛肉火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连雏菊都在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到Packy竟然会这么好卖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道为什么  突然就想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒你…难不成没买到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么变成你吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸之后又来女祸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想玩的话  Packy什么的就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没关系的  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得还有一个卖Packy的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创业100年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小胡同里偷偷经营着的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个只有少数人知道的幻之点心店的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有卖剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大小姐  我一定会在晚饭前买回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以请您再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之点心店么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是过期食品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…只是个点心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟让他那么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packy什么的其实根本没所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我不知为什么也觉得想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个原因  小飒就被使唤来使唤去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有货了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？西泽同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒为什么会在这创业100年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小胡同里偷偷经营着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有少数人知道的幻之点心店里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该请她让给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  说的出口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西泽小姐也是特意跑来这创业100年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小胡同里偷偷经营着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有少数人知道的幻之点心店来买Packy的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…为了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能变成恶鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西…西泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  超喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后小飒为了买Packy跑遍了周围的市县  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了世界尽头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得小飒他好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该叫他回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…  连通讯手段都失去了的小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会就这样放弃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Combat Butler！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  他…准备将Packy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将Packy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将Packy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服了重重困难  终于得到了Packy呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说很明显是仿造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就姑且认同他的努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒的Packy  不要吃太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  我现在就把Packy送到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒…小飒…小飒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  小飒他  小飒他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒出车祸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻赶往现场  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽三千院家的所有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我没让他去买Packy的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  晚了一点  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  这样不行的啊  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好回房里躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好解释一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点被卡车撞是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为手里拿着足球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然奇迹般地毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如朋友般  足球救了我一命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大空翼的名言：足球是朋友）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  尽让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个…Packy嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卡车压了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这根已经是尽了全力的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  摄像头坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是大小姐的管家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大小姐的想法了如直掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packy也吃到了  这下大小姐可以安心睡觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你也是  累了的话就回房间睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我会陪在大小姐身边直到您睡着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是让他买个Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让人担心成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没出息的管家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且带回来的Packy只有一根
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那根Packy是世界第一的美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始就是新学期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是新学期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微撒娇一下  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  放开了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:22:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…  伊澄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果分到一个班的话  就请多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指教什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指教什么…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？新学期刚开学就要告白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连你也在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新学期伊始之际
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔的讲话  太长了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好听人讲话的话  会被揍的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  今天又能和大小姐一起上学了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊  难道我感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多也该咳完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去学校了哦  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎么说得好像是我在装病一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊得这么精神  就算生病也给我上学去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
